<p>Feature scaling is important to normalize the range of independent variables or features of the data. In this case, we will use <code>StandardScaler</code> which standardizes features by removing the mean and scaling to unit variance. It's applied <em>after</em> splitting to prevent data leakage from the test set into the training process.</p></span></div>
